comments: Coffey (LAC) clamps and pulls Tate's (HOU) inside arm and the contact affects his ability to get to the pass.
Tate (HOU) dislodges Coffey (LAC) from his position during the loose ball.
Schroder (HOU) makes a bad pass that results in a turnover.
Zubac (LAC) and Tate (HOU) briefly get tangled during the pick and the contact is marginal.
Jackson (LAC) and Wood (HOU) mutually engage and disengage off ball.
Tate (HOU) engages with Zubac (LAC) and makes incidental contact during the rebound.
Zubac (LAC) and Green (HOU) mutually engage during the loose ball.

Replay review of the shooting foul called on Zubac (LAC) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Zubac (LAC) makes marginal contact to Wood's (HOU) body after he legally contest his shot attempt near the rim.
Schroder (HOU) commits a take foul on Jackson (LAC).
Mann (LAC) legally contests Green's (HOU) jump shot attempt.
Wood (HOU) commits a take foul on Coffey (LAC).
